Package com.github.sahasatvik.math

This package contains ExpressionParser, along with all of the classes requires by it.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExpressionParser
    ExpressionParser provides methods for evaluating mathematical expressions, specifically tailored for parsing with this library.
    MathParser
    MathParser contains methods for solving simple operations involving arithmetic operators and functions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExpressionParserException
    Superclass of all Exceptions thrown by ExpressionParser.
    FunctionNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when an unparsable function is passed to ExpressionParser.
    MissingOperandException
    Exception thrown when an expression passed to ExpressionParser has a missing operand.
    NullExpressionException
    Exception thrown when an expression passed to ExpressionParser is empty.
    UnmatchedBracketsException
    Exception thrown when an expression passed to ExpressionParser has unmatched brackets.
    VariableNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when an unrecognized variable is passed to ExpressionParser.

Package com.github.sahasatvik.math Description

This package contains ExpressionParser, along with all of the classes requires by it. ExpressionParser is a simple expression parsing library, which parses a String representation of a mathematical expression into an evaluated answer.
Since:
1.0
Version:

Author:
